wiki.summary: Released on New Years Day in 2020, “20/20“ is Lil Tjay ode to the new decade. A play on the year 2020, “20/20“ is a reference to perfect vision. Tjay alludes to the fact that he has perfect vision for his future and his goals. He raps on his newfound fame and touches on his major goals for the upcoming year. In the week ending January 18, 2020, the track debuted and peaked at #94 on the Billboard Hot 100. Read more on Last.fm.
